::Dollen::

        Dollen kept kissing GoldenEye, not wanting the kiss to stop.  But,
then, another image of the beautiful fem bot streaked through his mind.  He
stopped.

            "Hey, uh, maybe we should get back to base.  I can pass on
eating," he paused, and smiled, "Or maybe, we should stay here for a bit
longer," He said and started kissing GoldenEye again.
